{"tid":16971,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"從你的廁所帶走馬桶是我","createTime":"2016-12-01T15:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T14:28:29.000Z","uid":13541,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2bd4d5695d71ba35453c3f69317b3cf8762e2a","tid":16971,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"召喚雪人巴同其他巴打繼續出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為何坐過那廁所板無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間怎麼這麼快沒廁所水<br />\n為何每次你要抆屎還有幾千格<br />\n轉手到我竟找不到廁紙<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你　仍然尚未發覺<br />\n出公廁屙得更寫意<br />\n時時漏夜撞入女廁<br />\n將一打M巾帶走　循環做廁紙<br />\n<br />\n在你的數簿放低廁板是我<br />\n算是暗中　Claim幾千蚊去出火<br />\n從你的廁所帶走馬桶是我<br />\n你坐過的　至少我都坐過</blockquote>"},{"pid":"047704fd0891d1b3bbd20699753b5fb06080c8cf","tid":16971,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71406b950b36ed72bb59f10f754fe81831dee95","tid":16971,"uid":26176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"建議進修聲樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d118502afa83580e361efb3a1412f0cc6af679f3","tid":16971,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議進修聲樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073c4d770497609a407934e740e05d4476121a67","tid":16971,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議進修聲樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8771087b3179c8186d3e5e29a804d991b4b2183b","tid":16971,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"屎尿屁 低質到不行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc6dbf47a8a9b5939d44490d60a964c33bc5cc3","tid":16971,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屎尿屁 低質到不行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d887720b4a987aa5724469cfca0059d2e68984","tid":16971,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屎尿屁 低質到不行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抆咗一次屎咋喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21391f2d5b99a49c34ba39b3a2be85c29fac8286","tid":16971,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285edb60f6b3867c31feb8b949c84424c284ea1f","tid":16971,"uid":49462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>召喚雪人巴同其他巴打繼續出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為何坐過那廁所板無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間怎麼這麼快沒廁所水<br />\n為何每次你要抆屎還有幾千格<br />\n轉手到我竟找不到廁紙<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你　仍然尚未發覺<br />\n出公廁屙得更寫意<br />\n時時漏夜撞入女廁<br />\n將一打M巾帶走　循環做廁紙<br />\n<br />\n在你的數簿放低廁板是我<br />\n算是暗中　Claim幾千蚊去出火<br />\n從你的廁所帶走馬桶是我<br />\n你坐過的　至少我都坐過</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為何擦過那抹手紙 無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間彷佛 增添了數格公廁<br />\n為何每次你好想屙尿 卻找不到<br />\n尿斗到底起撚 左去邊<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你 仍然尚未發覺<br />\n點解會多左兩三格<br />\n原來誤會撞入女廁<br />\n仆街了急急腳走 然後瀨了屎"},{"pid":"e8474bcdbb073f726451f0814973a6f567998e90","tid":16971,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>召喚雪人巴同其他巴打繼續出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為何坐過那廁所板無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間怎麼這麼快沒廁所水<br />\n為何每次你要抆屎還有幾千格<br />\n轉手到我竟找不到廁紙<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你　仍然尚未發覺<br />\n出公廁屙得更寫意<br />\n時時漏夜撞入女廁<br />\n將一打M巾帶走　循環做廁紙<br />\n<br />\n在你的數簿放低廁板是我<br />\n算是暗中　Claim幾千蚊去出火<br />\n從你的廁所帶走馬桶是我<br />\n你坐過的　至少我都坐過</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為何擦過那抹手紙 無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間彷佛 增添了數格公廁<br />\n為何每次你好想屙尿 卻找不到<br />\n尿斗到底起撚 左去邊<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你 仍然尚未發覺<br />\n點解會多左兩三格<br />\n原來誤會撞入女廁<br />\n仆街了急急腳走 然後瀨了屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fc4d53d448def463e2432ca4ae8f560011d32d","tid":16971,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}